criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Written and signed informed consent;

          -  native Italian-speaking patients or either sex;

          -  patients suffering from Parkinson's disease ranging from mild to severe, based on
             clinical judgement;

          -  presence of a native Italian-speaking caregiver.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with evidence of other central nervous system disorders;

          -  patients with a degree of depression or dementia which may prevent and/or affect
             ratings.
